<h1 class="govuk-heading-l datagovuk-heading-l">Council tax statistics</h1>

<p class="govuk-body-m datagovuk-body">Get statistics on:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li>Council Tax rates levels set by English local authorities since 2011</li>
<li>Council Tax and national non-domestic rates collection rates since 2009</li>
<li>Council Tax precepts for town and parish councils in England since 2010 </li>

</ul>
<p class="govuk-body-m datagovuk-body">You can also view and download live tables providing:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li>Band D Council Tax figures</li>
<li>average Council Tax per dwelling</li>
<li>Council Tax statistics for parish and town councils</li>

</ul>



